# Work Plans

- `active/` — task plans currently in progress. See
  [docs/ai/planning-and-work-logs.md](../docs/ai/planning-and-work-logs.md)
  for what goes in one and when to create it.
- `archive/` — completed task plans kept for historical record. Not every
  completed plan is archived — only ones with durable value; otherwise
  delete on completion.
- `templates/task-plan.md` — starting structure for a new plan.

Don't let `active/` accumulate stale plans — a plan sitting here implies
work is still in progress.
